<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA39">
<l>piḻaikka muyaṉṟōmō neñcamē pēcāy</l>
<l>taḻaikkun tuḻāymārvaṉ ṟaṉṉai yaḻaittorukāṟ</l>
<l>pōyupakā rampoliyak koḷḷā tavaṉ pukaḻē</l>
<l>vāyupakā ramkoṇṭa vāyppu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did we make an effort so as to fail, o heart? Speak,</l>
<l>one time invoking the one with thriving Tulsi on [his] chest,</l>
<l>going, without taking help to flourish, [to fail] the opportunity</l>
<l>that take the help of the mouth, that is, praise of him?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
